         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne ¶ 1/12/73 ¶  ¶ The expenditure of £100, dear Mr Bentham, for the next volume ¶  has been authorized formally. If you get no intimation of its being placed at your disposal already by this ma...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">73.12.01a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To George Bentham</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RBG Kew, Kew correspondence, Australia, Mueller, 1871-81, f. 132.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1/12/73</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The expenditure of £100, dear Mr Bentham, for the next volume<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">The Victorian Government's payment to Bentham for his work on </seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; font-style: italic; ">Flora australiensis </seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">was</seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; font-style: italic; "> </seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">included in the 'Additional</seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; font-style: italic; "> </seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">Estimates for 1873-4', approved on 28 October 1873 (Victoria, </seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; font-style: italic; ">Parliamentary Debates</seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">, vol. 17, session 1873, pp 2070-71).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> has been authorized formally. If you get no intimation of its being placed at your disposal already by this mail, you will be sure to get such by the next, or if not you need only place yourself in communication with the hon. Archibald Michie, Q.C., the present Agent General of Victoria in London.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I cannot imagine what became of the Australian specimens of Bischoffia Javanic[a]<seg style="font-weight: bold; "> </seg>and at least one Aporosa.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See G. Bentham to M, 24 September 1873.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> Perhaps they were mislaid here, what will be pardonable through the narrowness of space here</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Let me trust that you health is firm. I was much gladdened when I saw by last mail, that the 6th vol. had been brought to a conclusion by your unceasing exertions.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="">See G. Bentham to M, 24 September 1873.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>As yet I have no bill of loading of the case with <name key="Haemodoraceae%20">Haemodoraceae </name>&amp;c. Will you kindly enquire by what ship the return sending of that portion of the collection has been effected.<note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation, possibly by Hooker: '<seg style="font-style: italic; "> </seg>K[osciusko] | July'. Cf. G. Bentham to M, 27 August 1873: 'I trust that you will have received safe the Monocotyledons which were sent I believe by the Kosciusko'. <seg style="color: #000000; font-style: italic; ">Kosciusko</seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; "> began to unload cargo at Williamstown on 14 October 1873 (</seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>
                     <seg style="color: #000000; ">, 15 October 1873, p. 4). <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The case was presumably waiting to be collected when M wrote.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully always </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <name key="Aporosa%20">Aporosa </name>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">
                  <name key="Bischoffia%20Javanica%20">Bischoffia Javanica </name>
               </seg>
            </p>
